Package: tinylog
Title: Lightweight Script Registry for R Projects
Version: 0.0.0.9004
Authors@R:
    person("Tomas", "Reivinger", , "tomas.reivinger@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tracks which scripts produced which output files by maintaining a
    YAML registry. Two functions cover the full workflow: register_script()
    records metadata at the top of a script, and record_output() wraps any
    save call to log the output path.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    yaml
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 8.0.0
URL: https://github.com/tomasrei/tinylog
BugReports: https://github.com/tomasrei/tinylog/issues
